# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DSB Law Group — Resend email configuration (DUMMY DOMAIN)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# This project uses a PLACEHOLDER domain for documentation and local testing.
# You do NOT need a real domain to develop — emails print to the console.
#
# ── Dummy domain details ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   Company:     DSB Law Group
#   Domain:      dsblawgroup.com          (fictional — replace with yours)
#   Website:     https://www.dsblawgroup.com
#   Send from:   DSB Law Group <noreply@dsblawgroup.com>
#   Reply to:    info@dsblawgroup.com
#   Admin seed:  admin@gmail.com           (local login only, not email)
#
# ── What each variable does ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   RESEND_API_KEY       API key from https://resend.com/api-keys
#   RESEND_FROM_DOMAIN   Domain verified in Resend (must match From address)
#   EMAIL_FROM_NAME      Display name in inbox (e.g. "DSB Law Group")
#   EMAIL_FROM_ADDRESS   Local part before @ (usually noreply or hello)
#   EMAIL_FROM           Full From header (overrides NAME + ADDRESS if set)
#   EMAIL_REPLY_TO       Where replies go (e.g. info@yourfirm.com)
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL Links inside emails (verify, reset password, etc.)
#
# ── Local development (no Resend account needed) ─────────────────────────────
#
#   1. Copy these lines into D:\Bhupinder\nextjs\.env
#   2. Leave RESEND_API_KEY empty
#   3. Run npm run dev — register / reset password / subscribe
#   4. Check the terminal for [dev email] output with full HTML + links
#
# ── When you get a real domain (production checklist) ──────────────────────────
#
#   1. Buy domain (e.g. dsblaw.com or dsblawgroup.in)
#   2. Create free account at https://resend.com
#   3. Resend → Domains → Add domain → add DNS records (SPF, DKIM) at registrar
#   4. Resend → API Keys → Create → copy key starting with re_
#   5. Update .env on VPS:
#        RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_real_key_here
#        RESEND_FROM_DOMAIN=your-real-domain.com
#        EMAIL_FROM="DSB Law Group <noreply@your-real-domain.com>"
#        EMAIL_REPLY_TO=info@your-real-domain.com
#        NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://www.your-real-domain.com
#   6. Restart web + worker: docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml restart web worker
#
# ── Dummy values (copy into .env) ─────────────────────────────────────────────

RESEND_API_KEY=""
RESEND_FROM_DOMAIN="dsblawgroup.com"
EMAIL_FROM_NAME="DSB Law Group"
EMAIL_FROM_ADDRESS="noreply"
EMAIL_FROM="DSB Law Group <noreply@dsblawgroup.com>"
EMAIL_REPLY_TO="info@dsblawgroup.com"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL="https://www.dsblawgroup.com"

# Example fake API key format (DO NOT use — replace with real key from Resend):
# RESEND_API_KEY="re_123456789_dummy_example_replace_me"
